## Introduction
WeatherApp is a simple application that provides weather information for different locations.

## Features
- Current weather conditions
- 5-day weather forecast
- Search by city name

## Links
- [GitHub Repository](https://github.com/smoenter/Challenge-9-Weather-App)
- https://challenge-9-weather-app.onrender.com


## Installation
To install the WeatherApp, follow these steps:
1. Clone the repository (git clone https://github.com:smoenter/Challenge-9-Weather-App.git)
2. Navigate to the project directory (cd WeatherApp)
3. Install the dependencies (npm install)

## Usage
To use the WeatherApp, follow these steps:
1. Open the application
2. Enter the city name in the search bar
3. View the weather information

## Contributing
If you would like to contribute to the WeatherApp, please follow these guidelines:
1. Fork the repository
2. Create a new branch
3. Make your changes
4. Submit a pull request

